column16: Starlin Castro singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Charlie Culberson.
Matt Joyce singles on a ground ball to left fielder Curtis Granderson.   Ozzie Albies scores.    Tyler Flowers to 2nd.
Ozzie Albies triples (3) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Rosell Herrera.
Aaron Hicks doubles (2) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Jordan Luplow.   Cameron Maybin scores.
Cameron Maybin doubles (6) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Oscar Mercado.
Martin Prado doubles (7) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Ronald Acuna.   Harold Ramirez scores.
Harold Ramirez singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Ronald Acuna.
John Hicks singles on a line drive to center fielder Byron Buxton.
Teoscar Hernandez doubles (6) on a ground ball to right fielder Tim Locastro.
